{{ thought_balloon }} <b>Update pyTMBot (Docker Compose)</b>

<b>Recommended steps:</b>

1) Open directory with your <code>compose.yaml</code>
2) Pull fresh image
3) Recreate service
4) Check status and recent logs

<pre>cd /opt/pytmbot
docker compose pull pytmbot
docker compose up -d --force-recreate pytmbot
docker compose ps
docker compose logs -n 50 pytmbot</pre>

<b>Optional cleanup:</b>
<code>docker image prune -f</code>

ℹ️ <i>Your mounted config/secrets are preserved.</i>
